data.text: 24 hours post vaccination! I still feel really good! No side effects at all. Upper arm is now a little sore (but I did also sleep on that arm lol oops) - Feeling really good!

4 hours post vaccination and time for my first surgery check in: feel totally fine! Good actually! I took a Tylenol and iced my arm right after for about 5-10 minutes and I don’t feel any side effects. Normally my arm will be sore for days after flu shot but feels fine!
